'''Carida: Heavy Duty''' was a set of articles written by [[Cory J. Herndon]] for the [[Wizards.com]] ''[[Planet Hoppers]]'' web feature as part of [[Wizards of the Coast]]'s ''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game]]''. The four articles, released weekly starting on [[September 4]], [[2003]], focus on the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire's]] [[Carida Academy/Legends|Academy of Carida]].

==Contents==
===Part 1: Weight Training===
''&hellip;a [[Myrette Davani|future TIE pilot]] transfers to the [[Carida Academy/Legends|Carida Imperial Military Academy]] for her final [[Standard year/Legends|year]] of study.''<ref name="Carida" />

===Part 2: Boot Camp===
''&hellip;the fourth-year [[Cadet/Legends|cadets]] take part in combat exercises designed to cull the weak from the [[Palpatine/Legends|Emperor's]] [[Imperial Military/Legends|forces]].''<ref name="Carida" />

===Part 3: War Games===
''&hellip;cadets Davani and [[Lumiya|Brie]] take the new [[Mountain Terrain Scout Transport|MT-ST]] out for a crawl in the mountains of [[Carida/Legends|Carida]].''<ref name="Carida" />

===Part 4: Cadets Gone Wild===
''&hellip;cadets Davani and Brie have a wild night on a two-day pass before they graduate.''<ref name="Carida" />

